==English==

===Etymology===
*(noun) From Old French ''riule,'' from Vulgar Latin ''regula'' "straight stick, bar, ruler, pattern"
*(verb) From Old French ''riuler'', from Latin ''regulare''.

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-rule.ogg|Audio (US)}}
